Set Shell "zsh"
Set Width 1200
Set Height 400
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set FontSize 16
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

Output gifs/key-public.gif

Hide
Type "export PS1='darren@ForgeSworn.dev:bray $ '"
Enter
Type "alias claude=/Users/darren/WebstormProjects/bray/site/demos/bray-demo.sh"
Enter
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 0.5s
Show

Type "claude -p 'Use the key-public tool to get the public key for the current active identity'"
Enter
Sleep 25s
